reviews.text: The problem start when u see students working on. They always are wrong with your order. Students do not always work at this McDonalds but its summer for real it's a chaos

McDonalds located right outside FanLing MRT station. They have all the regular items plus a McCafe for specialty items. Busy during peak meal times, so you might have trouble finding a seat. Faster service than other McDonald's locations in Hong Kong. Expect to pay 20-40 $HKD per person.
Tasty burger but not piping hot. Chips was crispy, hot and look to have been cooked in fresh oil. Would have been 5 star if burger was hotter.
No electronic ordering and right by the station. So ever busy!
Excellent mc donalds

result.name: 麥當勞

reviews.text: 雖然人流多，但食物飲品預早做得太多，薯條炸唔熟，汽水冰溶曬
可以，除了部分位置冷氣太猛。
極之落後，沒有訂單機，沒有開水機，要用人手，時常沒有水，員工沒有空添加。

每日都要留意新餐牌,今日發現麥當奴有新發現,都麥當勞有無限智慧,可以日日新款😆

早前連續二日下午茶時段,試過二種新款漢堡,任何時間都多人買, 星期六,日仲多人,排隊後等餐也快, 分別有炸雞漢堡,吉列豬扒漢堡,二種試完後,感覺吉列豬扒漢堡好似較好,因為肉較厚身,俾豬柳飽好,天氣凍加上熱朱古力回家食.

今日再試埋锋味漢堡包,好大個🍔😆

好彩這些餐等待時間較快,所以如果趕時間朋友,也可以叫這些餐,一試無妨.
